      "title": "Numbered Discourses 5 ",
      "expandable": false
    },
    {
      "segments": [
        {
          "scid": "an5.308-1152:1.1",
          "pli": "“Rāgassa, bhikkhave, pariññāya … parikkhayāya … pahānāya … khayāya … vayāya … virāgāya … nirodhāya … cāgāya … paṭinissaggāya pañca dhammā bhāvetabbā. ",
          "en": "“For the complete understanding … finishing … giving up … ending … vanishing … fading away … cessation … giving away … letting go of greed, five things should be developed.” "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an5.308-1152:1.2",
          "pli": "Dosassa … mohassa … kodhassa … upanāhassa … makkhassa … paḷāsassa … issāya … macchariyassa … māyāya … sāṭheyyassa … thambhassa … sārambhassa … mānassa … atimānassa … madassa … pamādassa abhiññāya … pariññāya … parikkhayāya … pahānāya … khayāya … vayāya … virāgāya … nirodhāya … cāgāya … paṭinissaggāya pañca dhammā bhāvetabbā. (6–849.) ",
          "en": "“Of hate … delusion … anger … hostility … offensiveness … contempt … jealousy … stinginess … deceit … deviousness … obstinacy … aggression … conceit … arrogance … vanity … negligence … for insight … complete understanding … finishing … giving up … ending … vanishing … fading away … cessation … giving away … letting go … five things should be developed. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an5.308-1152:2.1",
          "pli": "Katame pañca? ",
          "en": "What five? "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an5.308-1152:2.2",
          "pli": "Saddhābalaṃ, vīriyabalaṃ, satibalaṃ, samādhibalaṃ, paññābalaṃ—",
          "en": "The powers of faith, energy, mindfulness, immersion, and wisdom. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an5.308-1152:2.3",
          "pli": "pamādassa, bhikkhave, paṭinissaggāya ime pañca dhammā bhāvetabbā”ti. (850) ",
          "en": "For the letting go of negligence, these five things should be developed.” "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an5.308-1152:2.4",
          "pli": "Rāgapeyyālaṃ niṭṭhitaṃ. ",
          "en": " "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an5.308-1152:3.1",
          "pli": "Abhiññāya pariññāya parikkhayāya, ",
          "en": " "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an5.308-1152:3.2",
          "pli": "Pahānāya khayāya vayena ca; ",
          "en": " "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an5.308-1152:3.3",
          "pli": "Virāganirodhā cāgañca, ",
          "en": " "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an5.308-1152:3.4",
          "pli": "Paṭinissaggo ime dasāti. ",
          "en": " "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an5.308-1152:3.5",
          "pli": "Pañcakanipāto niṭṭhito. ",
          "en": " "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an5.308-1152:4.1",
          "pli": "Sekhabalaṃ balañceva, ",
          "en": " "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an5.308-1152:4.2",
          "pli": "Pañcaṅgikañca sumanaṃ; ",
          "en": " "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an5.308-1152:4.3",
          "pli": "Muṇḍanīvaraṇañca saññañca, ",
          "en": " "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an5.308-1152:4.4",
          "pli": "Yodhājīvañca aṭṭhamaṃ; ",
          "en": " "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an5.308-1152:4.5",
          "pli": "Theraṃ kakudhaphāsuñca, ",
          "en": " "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an5.308-1152:4.6",
          "pli": "Andhakavindadvādasaṃ; ",
          "en": " "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an5.308-1152:4.7",
          "pli": "Gilānarājatikaṇḍaṃ, ",
          "en": " "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an5.308-1152:4.8",
          "pli": "Saddhammāghātupāsakaṃ; ",
          "en": " "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an5.308-1152:4.9",
          "pli": "Araññabrāhmaṇañceva, ",
          "en": " "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an5.308-1152:4.10",
          "pli": "Kimilakkosakaṃ tathā; ",
          "en": " "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an5.308-1152:4.11",
          "pli": "Dīghācārāvāsikañca, ",
          "en": " "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an5.308-1152:4.12",
          "pli": "Duccaritūpasampadanti. ",
          "en": " "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an5.308-1152:4.13",
          "pli": "Pañcakanipātapāḷi niṭṭhitā. ",
          "en": "The Book of the Fives is finished."
        }
      ],
